{
  "texts": [
    "Decision trees are sensitive to small perturbations in the trained data.",
    "Random Forest is an ensemble learning that parallel builds multiple random decision trees, and the prediction is based on the most voted by the trees.",
    "Random forest required more training time compared to other machine learning techniques.",
    "Conditional random field (CRF) is an undirected graphical model, and it has high performance on text and high dimensional data.",
    "CRF builds an observation sequence and is modelled based on conditional probability."
  ]
}